Meyer Burger Holds 32.38% of the Share Capital of Roth & Rau

-- B y   P a u l   V e r s c h u u r
-- 
2011-06-08T04:30:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-08/meyer-burger-holds-32-38-of-the-share-capital-of-roth-rau.html
Meyer Burger Technology Ltd. said it
held 32.38 percent of  Roth & Rau AG (R8R)  after its offer for the
German company ended on June 3.  The acceptance period was extended until June 22, Meyer
Burger said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Verschuur at 
 pverschuur@bloomberg.net  